<p><b>Carl Friedrich Gauss</b> neɣ Kaɣl Fxedxic Gawss s teqbaylit; yettwanṭaq <sup><span typeof="mw:File"><a href="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a1/De-carlfriedrichgauss.ogg"><img alt="Asusru n tsiwelt tadra" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loudspeaker.svg/20px-Loudspeaker.svg.png" decoding="async" width="11" height="11" class="mw-file-element" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loudspeaker.svg/22px-Loudspeaker.svg.png 2x" data-file-width="20" data-file-height="20"></a></span></sup>, ilul ass n 30 <a href="/wiki/Yebrir" title="Yebrir">Yebrir</a> aseggas n 1777 di Brunswick, yemmut ass n 23 di <a href="/wiki/Fu%E1%B9%9Ba%E1%B9%9B" class="mw-redirect" title="Fuṛaṛ">Fuṛaṛ</a> useggas n 1855 di Guttingen. Yella d amusnak ameqqran, d amesnallum u d amussnagamaw. Yesɛa tasmedna tameqrant, yebwid tummutin yesɛan azal s waṭas di tusniwin agi i d-nebder (nuder) qqaren-as <i>Ageldun n tusnakt</i>, d yiwen seg imusnaken imeqqranen n yal akud. <div style="position:absolute; left:40px; top:2px; width:95%;"><h2 id="Tazwart" style="margin:0; border-bottom:0; font-size:120%; font-weight:bold; text-align:left; color:#000; padding:.15em .4em;" class="mw-html-heading">Tazwart</h2></div></div>
</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><div style="margin:0em 1em 1em 1em; padding-right:0px; padding-top:12px;">
<p><b>Wikipedia</b> d asenfaṛ n tasanayt tamazdayt iserkeben ɣef Internet, tameɣradit, agettutlayt dɣa tessexdem s amenzay n <a href="/wiki/Wiki" title="Wiki">wiki</a>. Amesɣaru n Wikipedia d tufka n ugbur ilelli. Yal yiwen yezmer ad t-iseqdec, ad t-ibeddel, ad t-isileɣ.
</p><p>Asegrer n usenfaṛ agi i sbadu s <a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Imenzayen_imsnulfuyen&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Wikipedia:Imenzayen imsnulfuyen (ulac asebter)">imenzayen imsnulfuyen</a>. Agbur-is i seḥbiber s <span class="plainlinks"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.fr">licence <span class="lang-en" lang="en">Creative Commons by-sa</span></a></span> dɣa yezmer ad yilli <a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Citation_et_r%C3%A9utilisation_du_contenu_de_Wikipedia&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Wikipedia:Citation et réutilisation du contenu de Wikipedia (ulac asebter)">yenɣel s turagt nni</a> — ɣas ma i amesɣaru amzenzi — s leqdar n tiwtiltin.
</p><p>Imira, <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia" title="Wikipedia">Wikipedia s teqbaylit</a> i ttkel 6 997 imagraden.
</p>
<div style="text-align:right;"><a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Awal_%C9%A3ef...&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Wikipedia:Awal ɣef... (ulac asebter)">Awal ɣef Wikipedia</a> <b>•</b> <a href="/wiki/Wikipedia" title="Wikipedia">Amnir ɣef Wikipedia</a></div></div>
</td></tr>

<tr>
<td>

</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><div style="margin:0em 1em 1em 1em; padding-right:0px; padding-top:12px;">
<p>Yal yiwen yezmer ad yernu s udwal agbur s weskar uqqin, ilaq kan ilugan ad illin qaderen; amedya: aselken n ugbur neɣ asidmer n imagraden.
</p>
Llan aṭas isebtaren n tallalt, ladɣa iwakken ad nesnulfu amagrad, ad nbeddel asebter neɣ ad ad nesɣer-d tugna. Tzemrem ad tsersem asteqsi.</div>
</td></tr>

</td></tr>
<tr>
<td><div style="margin:0em 1em 1em 1em; padding-right:0px; padding-top:12px;">
<p>Deg uɣrud, 15 702 imiḍanen n imseqdacen snulfan ɣef Wikipedia. Dɣa gar-asen, 25 llan urmiden deg ayyur aneggaru. Akk wid yesnulfan imagraden, sseqdacen s lbaṭel ; Sileɣen tajmaɛt tamazdayt, war aɣella, anda imedrawen Sersiyen ussisen-nsen deg <a href="/w/index.php?title=Asenfa%E1%B9%9B:Amager&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Asenfaṛ:Amager (ulac asebter)">isenfaṛen isentalen</a> dɣa d aṭas <a href="/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Abrid_n_ti%C9%A3lusin_d_ttberna&action=edit&redlink=1" class="new" title="Wikipedia:Abrid n tiɣlusin d ttberna (ulac asebter)">tallunin n amyannan</a>.
</p><p>Isqardecen d tamawin af imagraden: ansuf yis-sen! <a href="/wiki/Tallat:Amyannan" title="Tallat:Amyannan">Isebtaren n amyannan</a> seqdacen i ussegrew n tisnezgimin d timaduzin iwakken ad nsileɣ imagraden.
</p>

## Amagrad n wass  
---  
[![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9b/Carl_Friedrich_Gauss.jpg/120px-Carl_Friedrich_Gauss.jpg)](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tugna:Carl_Friedrich_Gauss.jpg) **Carl Friedrich Gauss** neɣ Kaɣl Fxedxic Gawss s teqbaylit; yettwanṭaq [![Asusru n tsiwelt tadra](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8a/Loudspeaker.svg/20px-Loudspeaker.svg.png)](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a1/De-carlfriedrichgauss.ogg), ilul ass n 30 [Yebrir](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yebrir "Yebrir") aseggas n 1777 di Brunswick, yemmut ass n 23 di [Fuṛaṛ](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fu%E1%B9%9Ba%E1%B9%9B "Fuṛaṛ") useggas n 1855 di Guttingen. Yella d amusnak ameqqran, d amesnallum u d amussnagamaw. Yesɛa tasmedna tameqrant, yebwid tummutin yesɛan azal s waṭas di tusniwin agi i d-nebder (nuder) qqaren-as _Ageldun n tusnakt_ , d yiwen seg imusnaken imeqqranen n yal akud. ([**Kemmel leqraya**...](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Carl_Friedrich_Gauss "Carl Friedrich Gauss"))

## Tazwart  
---  
**Wikipedia** d asenfaṛ n tasanayt tamazdayt iserkeben ɣef Internet, tameɣradit, agettutlayt dɣa tessexdem s amenzay n [wiki](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki "Wiki"). Amesɣaru n Wikipedia d tufka n ugbur ilelli. Yal yiwen yezmer ad t-iseqdec, ad t-ibeddel, ad t-isileɣ.  Asegrer n usenfaṛ agi i sbadu s [imenzayen imsnulfuyen](https://kab.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Imenzayen_imsnulfuyen&action=edit&redlink=1 "Wikipedia:Imenzayen imsnulfuyen \(ulac asebter\)"). Agbur-is i seḥbiber s [licence Creative Commons by-sa](http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/deed.fr) dɣa yezmer ad yilli [yenɣel s turagt nni](https://kab.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Citation_et_r%C3%A9utilisation_du_contenu_de_Wikipedia&action=edit&redlink=1 "Wikipedia:Citation et réutilisation du contenu de Wikipedia \(ulac asebter\)") — ɣas ma i amesɣaru amzenzi — s leqdar n tiwtiltin.  Imira, [Wikipedia s teqbaylit](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia "Wikipedia") i ttkel 6 997 imagraden.  [Awal ɣef Wikipedia](https://kab.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Awal_%C9%A3ef...&action=edit&redlink=1 "Wikipedia:Awal ɣef... \(ulac asebter\)") **•** [Amnir ɣef Wikipedia](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia "Wikipedia")  
![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8f/Bluebg_rounded2.png) ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Text-x-generic_with_pencil-2.svg/40px-Text-x-generic_with_pencil-2.svg.png)
## Attekki  
Yal yiwen yezmer ad yernu s udwal agbur s weskar uqqin, ilaq kan ilugan ad illin qaderen; amedya: aselken n ugbur neɣ asidmer n imagraden.  Llan aṭas isebtaren n tallalt, ladɣa iwakken ad nesnulfu amagrad, ad nbeddel asebter neɣ ad ad nesɣer-d tugna. Tzemrem ad tsersem asteqsi.  
![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8f/Bluebg_rounded2.png) ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cd/HSSamarbete.svg/40px-HSSamarbete.svg.png)  
Deg uɣrud, 15 702 imiḍanen n imseqdacen snulfan ɣef Wikipedia. Dɣa gar-asen, 25 llan urmiden deg ayyur aneggaru. Akk wid yesnulfan imagraden, sseqdacen s lbaṭel ; Sileɣen tajmaɛt tamazdayt, war aɣella, anda imedrawen Sersiyen ussisen-nsen deg [isenfaṛen isentalen](https://kab.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Asenfa%E1%B9%9B:Amager&action=edit&redlink=1 "Asenfaṛ:Amager \(ulac asebter\)") dɣa d aṭas [tallunin n amyannan](https://kab.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Wikipedia:Abrid_n_ti%C9%A3lusin_d_ttberna&action=edit&redlink=1 "Wikipedia:Abrid n tiɣlusin d ttberna \(ulac asebter\)").  Isqardecen d tamawin af imagraden: ansuf yis-sen! [Isebtaren n amyannan](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tallat:Amyannan "Tallat:Amyannan") seqdacen i ussegrew n tisnezgimin d timaduzin iwakken ad nsileɣ imagraden.  [Amager n tajmaɛt](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wikipedia:Tajma%C9%9Bt "Wikipedia:Tajmaɛt")

## Amagrad n wass  
---  
![⟨49⟩](https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tugna:Carl_Friedrich_Gauss.jpg) **Carl Friedrich Gauss** neɣ Kaɣl Fxedxic Gawss s teqbaylit; yettwanṭaq ![Asusru n tsiwelt tadra⟨50⟩](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/a/a1/De-carlfriedrichgauss.ogg), ilul ass n 30 Yebrir⟨51⟩ aseggas n 1777 di Brunswick, yemmut ass n 23 di Fuṛaṛ⟨52⟩ useggas n 1855 di Guttingen. Yella d amusnak ameqqran, d amesnallum u d amussnagamaw. Yesɛa tasmedna tameqrant, yebwid tummutin yesɛan azal s waṭas di tusniwin agi i d-nebder (nuder) qqaren-as _Ageldun n tusnakt_ , d yiwen seg imusnaken imeqqranen n yal akud. (**Kemmel leqraya**...⟨53⟩)

## Tazwart  
---  
**Wikipedia** d asenfaṛ n tasanayt tamazdayt iserkeben ɣef Internet, tameɣradit, agettutlayt dɣa tessexdem s amenzay n wiki⟨63⟩. Amesɣaru n Wikipedia d tufka n ugbur ilelli. Yal yiwen yezmer ad t-iseqdec, ad t-ibeddel, ad t-isileɣ.  Asegrer n usenfaṛ agi i sbadu s imenzayen imsnulfuyen⟨64⟩. Agbur-is i seḥbiber s licence Creative Commons by-sa⟨65⟩ dɣa yezmer ad yilli yenɣel s turagt nni⟨66⟩ — ɣas ma i amesɣaru amzenzi — s leqdar n tiwtiltin.  Imira, Wikipedia s teqbaylit⟨38⟩ i ttkel 6 997 imagraden.  Awal ɣef Wikipedia⟨67⟩ **•** Amnir ɣef Wikipedia⟨38⟩  
![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8f/Bluebg_rounded2.png) ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/b8/Text-x-generic_with_pencil-2.svg/40px-Text-x-generic_with_pencil-2.svg.png)
## Attekki  
Yal yiwen yezmer ad yernu s udwal agbur s weskar uqqin, ilaq kan ilugan ad illin qaderen; amedya: aselken n ugbur neɣ asidmer n imagraden.  Llan aṭas isebtaren n tallalt, ladɣa iwakken ad nesnulfu amagrad, ad nbeddel asebter neɣ ad ad nesɣer-d tugna. Tzemrem ad tsersem asteqsi.  
![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/8f/Bluebg_rounded2.png) ![](https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/cd/HSSamarbete.svg/40px-HSSamarbete.svg.png)  
Deg uɣrud, 15 702 imiḍanen n imseqdacen snulfan ɣef Wikipedia. Dɣa gar-asen, 25 llan urmiden deg ayyur aneggaru. Akk wid yesnulfan imagraden, sseqdacen s lbaṭel ; Sileɣen tajmaɛt tamazdayt, war aɣella, anda imedrawen Sersiyen ussisen-nsen deg isenfaṛen isentalen⟨68⟩ dɣa d aṭas tallunin n amyannan⟨69⟩.  Isqardecen d tamawin af imagraden: ansuf yis-sen! Isebtaren n amyannan⟨70⟩ seqdacen i ussegrew n tisnezgimin d timaduzin iwakken ad nsileɣ imagraden.  Amager n tajmaɛt⟨71⟩
